cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to detect verbal expression of aggression. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with detecting aggression, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
